title: We Answer Your Garbage Questions!
description:
Kippy and Foley are back with another family episode where they answer your AYG questions. The boys talk proper attire for a wedding, how to pierce your own ear, and what to do when you get a rash. Its a fun one! Thanks for listening!


Bonus Episodes: https://www.patreon.com/AreYouGarbage


T-Shirts: http://www.PodcastMerch.com 


Follow Kevin: https://www.instagram.com/kevinryancomedy/ 
Follow Foley: https://www.instagram.com/foleygrams/


Comedians H. Foley and Kevin Ryan are self proclaimed GARBAGE. Each week a new stand up comedian gets put to the test. Steal shampoo from hotels? Own a George Foreman Grill? Ever worn JNCO Jeans?
